Gemalto NV and International Business Machines Corp to Offer Enhanced eBanking Security Platform

Wednesday, 20 Nov 2013 01:00am EST

Gemalto NV announced a global business partnership with International Business Machines Corp for its enhanced Ezio eBanking security platform. Featuring cutting-edge levels of security and versatility, the Ezio eBanking Server platform has been further updated with the ability to support a wider range of end-user solutions. The platform has been tested and confirmed to work with more than 30 authentication devices from 20 different vendors, ranging from physical tokens to mobile applications. It is made available worldwide, directly from Gemalto and also through IBM Security Services.Â 

